{
  "stem": "27.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was in the Wehrmacht, you know, and really honest, I don't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you can have anything you want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I told her, we don't want anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm looking for something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she stayed in the kitchen-- listen to this one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to the bedroom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I opened the drawer, SS uniform, Gestapo uniform.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, you know, like this, in order.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not just thrown in, you know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could see it was just cleaned and ironed and everything over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Can you imagine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's an SS uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then we went over there, and we told them, what is this?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody knew nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I want you to understand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "No German knew there was a concentration camp, which is a lie.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They all knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some knew it more, some knew it less, but they all knew it because it was just in their background.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This happened after the order, you know, after liberation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I stayed there about for six weeks in Garmisch-Partenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There's who speaks English, a volunteer and we were distributors of the Red Cross packages.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Cheese and every-- naturally I had all I wanted when I was there already but everybody had.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There was no-- nobody died after liberation because of shortage, nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is not true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Not at least who was liberated by the US Army, nobody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And stayed there and then they said, well, you want to go home?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I go, sure, I want to go home, my mother is home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Even then you understand what a human being is?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Even then, maybe somebody came home, maybe a cousin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Of course, I want to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Anyway, OK, they load us on a truck and they took us to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
